==German==
===Etymology===
Analogous to [[Sozi]], a shortened form of the Bavarian surname [[Ignatius]], emphasizing the crude aspect of National Socialists. Probably ''not'' originally a shortened form of [[Nationalsozialist]], though the first two sillables sound exactly like ''Nazi''.
